<p>Your favorite Mac geeks celebrated their 200th episode by &#8220;airing&#8221; the taping of the show live on TalkShoe, complete with listener interaction. Great stuff here, as always, and the show has an interesting real-time vibe to it, as well! &nbsp;Topics include WiFi, Time Machine, Time Capsule, cron/launchd, Mouse acceleration, and more.</p>
